{"name":"Back up the database with Notion and Google Drive","nodes":[{"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"weeks","triggerAtDay":[5],"triggerAtHour":9}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"416450e4-2dfc-4076-aa22-a95d349cd707","name":"Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"operation":"download","fileId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"={{ $json.id || $json.fileId }}"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","typeVersion":3,"position":[54,400],"id":"f7672c8d-0ea5-4054-93a1-d173cb77de90","name":"Download from Google Drive","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"csv","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.extractFromFile","typeVersion":1,"position":[378,400],"id":"2e850325-036c-4c31-a32d-60a231912c8d","name":"Parse CSV Contents"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Normalize incoming payload records to a stable schema\nconst out = [];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const j = item.json;\n  out.push({ json: {\n    itemId: String(j.itemId ?? j.id ?? '').trim(),\n    source: typeof j.source === 'string' ? j.source.trim() : j.source ?? null,\n    source: j.source ?? 'api',\n    receivedAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n  } });\n}\nreturn out;"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[702,400],"id":"bb09c543-47d2-490a-b865-59740bfca093","name":"Clean & Reshape Rows"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"136f127a-0ae1-419c-b441-424d4865a463","leftValue":"={{ $json.itemId }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[1026,400],"id":"bbfc4b03-f1ac-442d-b316-aafc2a07eb12","name":"Rows Pass Validation?"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Payload Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[1350,880],"id":"770e3f82-15ac-4c77-9291-fee9fb53bbaf","name":"Quarantine Bad Rows","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"appendOrUpdate","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Payload Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":["itemId"],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1674,400],"id":"da90aa36-bfa8-4fc5-bbc6-a8e3b0af4517","name":"Load Rows into Google Sheets","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"xlsx","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.convertToFile","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[1998,400],"id":"8bb0942b-fdae-42f2-8f60-a89c1b8a4a77","name":"Repack as XLSX"},{"parameters":{"operation":"upload","name":"={{ 'processed-' + $now.toFormat('yyyyLLdd') + '.xlsx' }}","driveId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"My Drive"},"folderId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Processed"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","typeVersion":3,"position":[2322,400],"id":"8c7b5a2e-4138-40b8-97f4-9d0070e6069b","name":"Archive Processed File (Google Drive)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.source }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[2646,400],"id":"007d50ac-c129-48f3-944b-6a43e1dfd60c","name":"Enrich with Reference Data","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"9d7b560f-316b-4c01-9888-cc90c952707c","name":"enrichedAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"6443d857-ae41-4d31-a701-ba2e6122736b","name":"enrichmentSource","value":"reference-api","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[2970,400],"id":"03d1ff81-47d6-47a8-a18f-d00b48fd1c03","name":"Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"operation":"csv","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.convertToFile","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[3294,400],"id":"c58f0f60-b6f6-458d-b01c-cf1f6b5795d1","name":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"operation":"upload","name":"=run-{{ $now.toFormat('yyyyLLdd-HHmm') }}.csv","driveId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"My Drive"},"folderId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Archives"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","typeVersion":3,"position":[3618,400],"id":"0d5cb30b-5eca-4bca-b12d-a66a088fa610","name":"Archive Copy to Google Drive","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"read","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Payload Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[3942,400],"id":"7a37d310-1dab-4d84-9910-e45e087e9159","name":"Load Previous Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\nconst current = $input.first().json;\nconst prev = $('Load Previous Snapshot').first().json || {};\nconst drift = {};\nfor (const k of Object.keys(current)) {\n  if (typeof current[k] === 'number' && typeof prev[k] === 'number' && prev[k] !== 0) {\n    drift[k] = Math.round(((current[k] - prev[k]) / prev[k]) * 1000) / 10;\n  }\n}\nreturn [{ json: { ...current, driftPct: drift, hasDrift: Object.values(drift).some(v => Math.abs(v) > 10) } }];"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[4266,400],"id":"56cdf7a9-c68a-44bd-8278-1977c0c6f72c","name":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"completedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[4590,400],"id":"f7c7356d-90a4-4835-8904-8f897990eb5f","name":"Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"dataToSave":{"values":[{"key":"runId","value":"={{ $execution.id }}"},{"key":"itemCount","value":"={{ $items().length }}"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.executionData","typeVersion":1,"position":[4914,400],"id":"5659ce67-3aae-4168-80f5-a64b51aa78c9","name":"Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"6dbfada0-0ef5-4af3-b355-b2f348244379","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"94eabbc8-ea69-4c94-ad88-83cc53e2e5ad","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"a16c9110-bcfe-41fc-9a74-e3b8122add2a","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,400],"id":"0484edde-6581-4188-93a2-5d0bfbd632d8","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Payload Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[5562,400],"id":"849c587c-e1db-40b4-bf77-5eda35b8b231","name":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"authentication":"webhook","content":"=✅ Back up the database with Notion and Google Drive — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.discord","typeVersion":2,"position":[5886,400],"id":"fec38526-1f3b-4e91-83a2-a2d6e3f76f5f","name":"Send Summary to Discord","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"32ff4e46-55dc-472f-b490-b7eb2c5f813d","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"89dc4df9-26a1-4a25-9d16-13d0eff0b1dd","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"8cae58fc-747b-42be-afae-5fb09010952f","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,1420],"id":"229391bf-3512-4c17-99d6-438c56ff51aa","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"authentication":"webhook","content":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.discord","typeVersion":2,"position":[5562,1420],"id":"d292f4e3-9ec3-48e3-87a9-565759137855","name":"Escalate Failure to Discord","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Payload Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[5886,1420],"id":"261242ae-458f-472d-93a9-eb3333b374a2","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Download from Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"345a77bc-4f98-2f67-e36b-8da8f3e300d1","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Download from Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `download` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Parse CSV Contents · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"8312c769-7409-dc9b-852a-8323577ccba7","name":"Note: Download from Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Parse CSV Contents\n\nParses the incoming CSV binary into JSON items.\n\nNext: Clean & Reshape Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"0f27937d-fbf6-a2d9-458b-492fe8597d15","name":"Note: Parse CSV Contents"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Clean & Reshape Rows\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming payload records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Rows Pass Validation?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"e8d3702a-5e16-020e-5ab7-bebf1378673d","name":"Note: Clean & Reshape Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Rows Pass Validation?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.itemId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Rows into Google Sheets · ②→ Quarantine Bad Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"c7d4b691-81a5-b151-2e81-2621433b5276","name":"Note: Rows Pass Validation?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Quarantine Bad Rows\n\nnotion — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1000],"id":"f47e5ff8-8a5b-45b5-5d25-498b20b3379a","name":"Note: Quarantine Bad Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Rows into Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Repack as XLSX · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"1fa8a506-9620-9a91-98b5-c9c233e093c0","name":"Note: Load Rows into Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Repack as XLSX\n\nSerializes items to a XLSX binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Processed File (Google Drive)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"07efc4c1-4401-d13c-9776-be5402e80be4","name":"Note: Repack as XLSX"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Processed File (Google Drive)\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Enrich with Reference Data · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"fd742a6a-6c5a-d5cc-15c8-ed7711d5c638","name":"Note: Archive Processed File (Google Drive)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"bdd1f3d5-a1bf-927f-1986-70046829ac4d","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"70141035-5998-0ecf-1c8b-632e6d281ca6","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Copy to Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"505405e0-fdbb-d4ee-0943-93270e9e3767","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Copy to Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Previous Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"b4e57db9-ce9c-cff1-616d-7567a552b559","name":"Note: Archive Copy to Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"793f027f-9c40-f1b7-c0b5-f1f305e996c2","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"df8ef559-45d9-cfaf-6824-854d2a9aac26","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"8e39600a-30ff-6ceb-e723-77fff60641f3","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"07baa6fe-156c-50e4-96b3-27a565559f99","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"37c8eca9-14db-8297-d503-d13ff4c3620e","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Discord · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"b711922d-2186-c6ad-a117-d2147484e279","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Discord\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"bd4ed52e-3bad-d2a5-733f-07b344241c6c","name":"Note: Send Summary to Discord"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Discord","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,1540],"id":"8fb72340-0ee6-eed2-dc24-144c54919298","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Discord\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"0d4772d8-84e5-2458-95d6-ab99e2967ca4","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Discord"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,1540],"id":"34d281e0-dea1-fb83-0645-02691ebfdf90","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Back up the database with Notion and Google Drive\n\n**Pattern:** Backup & Archive · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nBack up the database with Notion and Google Drive. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual backups is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Download from Google Drive → Parse CSV Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Rows Pass Validation? → Load Rows into Google Sheets → Repack as XLSX → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to backup & archive without manual effort\n- Anyone automating backups in software development\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Discord webhook URL; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"bf70d011-7276-4a82-81d5-38e63fc41aa8","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"315f3b4f-304f-aed5-aa84-9b0b9e72fff0","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your backups process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"bd873fe6-7a0f-81a8-bb6b-093de6ee9699","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Download from Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Download from Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Parse CSV Contents","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","